mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query

Class DistributedRenderQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.query.AccumuloQuery
      • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.query.AccumuloFilteredIndexQuery
        • mil.nga.giat.geowave.accumulo.query.AccumuloConstraintsQuery
          • mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.query.DistributedRenderQuery

  • public class DistributedRenderQuery
extends AccumuloConstraintsQuery
    This class extends the capabilities of a simple constraints query to perform distributed rendering within tablet servers. It is able to serialize a distributed renderer and return a set of features that contain the rendered images ready for composition. It also supports CQL filters.
